        "notes": [
            {
                "category": "summary",
                "text": "NVIDIA has released software updates for NVIDIA\u00ae Jetson AGX Orin\u2122 series and NVIDIA IGX Orin. <br><div>To protect your system, download and install the latest release for Jetson AGX Orin series as part of the NVIDIA JetPack\u2122 software development kit (SDK) from <a href=\"https://developer.nvidia.com/embedded/downloads\">NVIDIA DevZone</a> and the latest release for IGX Orin as a new IGX OS ISO image from <a href=\"https://developer.nvidia.com/igx-downloads\">IGX Download Center</a>.</div>",
                "title": "Summary"
            },
            {
